content:
Gahahaha~! What is this, some kind of mind-reading magic?
Just when I receive exactly the gift I wished for...
Could it be that you're the Chrysovian Astralink?!{什么？}

I know it's a bit rude to expect presents from someone you just met{短暂停}
It's just a lickle impolite,
But you can't hide how excited you feel about it!

It's fine, yeah. {微笑}
Just my hopes and dreams being crushed, that's all~
I really don't mind, honestly. {微笑}

I'll let you in on a secret, {短暂停}
Actually, I have a surprise for you too!
This <color=#8AAB4B>{回礼}</color>!

...Oh, it's alive.
Thank you, I'll take good care of it...{短暂停}
Barring any special circumstances, it should survive at my place.

Let me open it and see, it's a <color=#8AAB4B>{礼物}</color>, {短暂停}
You really scared me there,
Interesting.

I have a guess, though I'm a bit shy to say it...
Um...{短暂停}
Were you just{短暂停}picking out a gift for me?

I'm sure there's still room at home,
and even if there isn't, I'll "make" some room
using "physical means." (Serious)

I plan to put it in the biggest fish tank there is—the ocean!{短暂停}
Just kidding.
I really like it and will take good care of it. Thank you!

If I told you I dreamed about you giving me a gift...
Would you laugh at me? {微笑}
Eh? You actually have a gift for me?!

A gift? If it's from you, {短暂停}
I'll gladly accept it, you sneaky thing.
I'll take care of it.

Hmm...{短暂停}
I think I might have misunderstood something,
Perhaps today isn't the best day to receive gifts.

Fish?{短暂停}
I wonder how it'll taste...
Thanks anyway!

Hmm...{短暂停}
I think I might have misunderstood something,
Perhaps today isn't the best day to receive gifts.

This... is, {短暂停}
delightful.
<color=#d3b037>{me}</color>, thank you.
